snippet.textDisplay:
When i used to be in college 8 yrs ago ,i met my bf and we used to bunk class and go to a nearby park where he'd just sit and admire me and sing the verse 3 of this song for me...Today I'm listening to this song after 8 yrs and it brought back all those memories,like it happened yesterday,i can still see him sitting in the park , holding my face and singing this song for me...🥺


P.s. we're about to get married next year 🧿
